                                                   rdfs:subClassOf <http://w3id.org/fio/v1/naics#NAICS-Industry> .


###  http://w3id.org/fio/v1/naics#NAICS-IndustrySector
<http://w3id.org/fio/v1/naics#NAICS-IndustrySector> rdf:type owl:Class ;
